18:07.480 --> 18:12.480
You must, all right, touch the feet of this Rahuri-Land.

18:17.780 --> 18:24.860
Then after, Ganesha, we must also touch the feet.

18:26.480 --> 18:30.070
As soon as I get the land, first we establish Ganesha here,

18:30.400 --> 18:32.030
and once this land, we get

18:32.190 --> 18:34.400
everywhere in the whole world, we get land

18:34.820 --> 18:38.440
and we have no problems of any kind as far as the land is concerned.

18:38.860 --> 18:42.440
When the Ashram is built here, everywhere in the whole world

18:42.820 --> 18:46.480
we’ll have Ashrams. So the beginning has to be at the right place.

